## Notes

- Entity reach in 1.21.1 is exposed via `class_3222#method_7349()` (entity-interaction range attribute).
- `method_5739(entity)` returns linear distance; `method_5858(entity)` is squared. We use squared to avoid the `sqrt`.
- The `entity.method_37908() == level` check defends against the (rare) case where `level.method_8469(id)` resolves to an entity marked in a different dimension during dimension transitions.
